{"author":{"id":"9ce646fd10346788b0ba0bb1d6d4d7df7faf6b71badbb76619d75576ac1df697"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770828908,"nonce":"melNN93OHdTsFKrcJzj1l2xM1YI=","title":"Borrower link shows 'Content missing' due to Turbo Frame mismatch","message":"Clicking a borrower name in /verwaltung shows 'Content missing' instead of navigating to the borrower detail page.\n\n**Root cause:** The borrower name links in _result_item.html.erb are inside \u003cturbo-frame id=\"results\"\u003e (from _search.html.erb:74). Turbo intercepts the click and looks for a matching frame in the borrowers/show response, which has no such frame.\n\n**Fix:** Add data-turbo-frame=\"_top\" to the link in app/views/borrowers/_result_item.html.erb:4 so it performs a full page navigation.\n\n**Affected file:** app/views/borrowers/_result_item.html.erb:4","files":null}]}